snippet.title: Supercut of the Indiepocalypse Game Anthology (Issue 01 to 04)
snippet.description:
Link to the article: https://game-curator.com/indie/indiepocalypse

Link to all issues of the game anthology: http://www.indiepocalypse.com

The cover art, which was used in the thumbnail, was made by KC Green. Follow him on Twitter: https://twitter.com/kcgreenn
